rs winchester has been a major global supplier of sporting ammunition and has long been the leader in introducing innovative new products conservation and hunter education we serve recreational shooters hunters law enforcement agencies and the us armed forcesread more epoxy olin epoxy is the leading global supplier of epoxy products formerly dow epoxy we are proud to continue to provide customers with the quality and reliability they have come to expect from us our leading technology has been the fundamental building block of robust solutions for diverse applications for more than  yearsread more chlorinated organics chlorinated organics is the largest global supplier of chlorinated organic products and services including solvents and intermediates our products are used in a variety of applications ranging from chemical processing dry cleaning metal cleaning and degreasing methyl cellulose paint formulation and stripping pharmaceuticals manufacturing quaternary ammonium compounds silicone production and urethane foam blowingread more welcome to olin olin corporation nyse oln has a long history of supplying quality products and services to our customers while generating value for our shareholders on a daily basis we are meeting our customers evolving needs through innovation and an unwavering commitment to exceeding expectations and maintaining the highest ethical standards olins  dedicated employees are also fully committed to being good neighbors and environmental stewards in the communities in which our facilities are located   olins  nd quarter earnings conference call will be held august   at am et              responsible care responsible care is a global initiative aimed at minimizing any negative impact from the manufacture distribution and use of chemicals while maximizing the beneficial use of our products in society our goal is to meet or exceed responsible care guidelines in every instance read more vision zero our winchester division is pursuing much the same goals through a new process called vision zero it is focused on improving environmental health and safety practices in the workplace read more recent events corporate office  carondelet plaza suite  clayton mo     privacy  careers nyse  oln       menu olin offers a variety of jobs and career paths that will appeal to those who are drawn to a creative energetic and open workplace environment olin is always interested in hiring the best and most enthusiastic talent available offering prospective employees exciting opportunities to grow and prosper within a dynamic company learn about available career opportunities in our career opportunities section olin is absolutely committed to diversity within its work force and to providing equal employment opportunities to all employees and job applicants this applies to every phase of the employment process  from hiring and training to compensation promotion and disciplinary action olin corporations chlor alkali and winchester divisions offer job opportunities for all qualified applicants including college students participating in coop plans inroads participants and skilled craftsmen   search job listings   recruiting scam advisory please be advised that unauthorized individuals may attempt to use the olin corporation “olin” name or brand as well as the name of olin directors and employees in an attempt to secure personal or financial information or money from job seekers   these scammers use a variety of tactics including posting false job postings on job boards and other locations and sending unsolicited emails text messages or other communications to job seekers falsely representing themselves to be affiliated with olin  the following are some important signs to look for in determining whether you may be the target of a scam check the email address origin olin employees should have an email address ending in olincom or olinbccom  scammers will try to make very similar email address domains so make sure to check that it is from a olincom or olinbccom address a communication requests money for placement fees recruiting or in exchange for guaranteed employment  any communication requesting any amount of money in exchange for employment with olin is fraudulent  olin never charges candidates fees or requires payments of any kind in order to secure employment a communication requests payment as a fee for certification training materials or other workrelated expenses olin does not require payment for any materials as part of its recruiting process requests for tax bank account or credit card information olin recruiters do not require the completion of tax forms or request bank account or credit card information as part of the recruiting process  as a precaution we recommend you do not disclose personal or financial details to anyone in response to an unsolicited email request offers work from home opportunities olin does not currently offer any work from home opportunities you may also have been contacted directly by a scammer who may have obtained your resume through a resume database as a federal contractor olin is committed to equal opportunity employment and all valid open positions will be posted on our website wwwolincom and all interested applicants must apply online  we do not accept paper applications except in limited circumstances and we do not directly solicit individuals for any role that is not posted on our website we do not conduct interviews via text or an instant messaging application like google hangout if you are contacted regarding a fraudulent employment proposal or have been the victim of a recruiting scam you are encouraged to alert your local law enforcement agency the federal trade commission also has a reporting service on their website for those who have been targeted by a recruiting scam    benefits olin salaried employees enjoy competitive salaries and generous benefits in a challenging and positive work atmosphere headquartered in clayton mo olin has major facilities in alabama california canada georgia illinois louisiana mississippi nevada new york and tennessee     college recruiting olin corporation is always looking for talented individuals to join our team we regularly recruit at certain college campuses throughout the us seeking individuals with the background energy and creativity that will carry our company forward if youre a college student nearing graduation and are interested in learning if your talents might fit with olin please visit our job listing section and apply online “olin is an equal opportunity employer and all qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race color religion sex sexual orientation gender identity national origin disability status protected veteran status or any other characteristic protected by law” latest news recent events corporate office  carondelet plaza suite  clayton mo     privacy  facility locations nyse  oln       menu facility locations olin corporation headquarters  carondelet plaza suite  clayton mo    chlor alkali products corporate office  stuart road ne cleveland tn    olin chlor alkali products  vinyls  old lower river road charleston tn    olin chlor alkali products  vinyls  doug barnard parkway augusta ga    olin chlor alkali products  vinyls  industrial road mcintosh al    olin chlor alkali products  vinyls  buffalo ave po box  niagara falls ny    olin chlor alkali products  vinyls  fourth street henderson nv   olin chlor alkali products  vinyls  pike street santa fe springs ca   olin chlor alkali products  vinyls  highway  st gabriel la                           olin chlor alkali products  vinyls  south banta road tracy ca   olin chlor alkali products  vinyls  alphonsedeshaies boulevard becancour quebec gh y   olin epoxy no nanjing road jiangsu yangtze river intl chemical park zhangjiaganag  china olin epoxy  gongdanro gil gumicity gyeongbuk kumi  south korea olin buetzflether sand   stade nd germany                      